{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I am the daughter of a forger,"},{"time":3916,"text":"not just any forger ..."},{"time":5861,"text":"When you hear the word \"forger,\" you often understand \"mercenary.\""},{"time":8778,"text":"You understand \"forged currency,\" \"forged pictures.\""},{"time":12300,"text":"My father is no such man."},{"time":14612,"text":"For 30 years of his life,"},{"time":15800,"text":"he made false papers --"},{"time":18502,"text":"never for himself, always for other people,"},{"time":20447,"text":"and to come to the aid of the persecuted and the oppressed."},{"time":24336,"text":"Let me introduce him."},{"time":26500,"text":"Here is my father at age 19."},{"time":29500,"text":"It all began for him during World War II,"},{"time":33500,"text":"when at age 17 he found himself thrust"},{"time":35500,"text":"into a forged documents workshop."},{"time":37200,"text":"He quickly became the false papers expert of the Resistance."},{"time":41700,"text":"And it's not a banal story --"},{"time":43500,"text":"after the liberation he continued"},{"time":46500,"text":"to make false papers until the '70s."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49600,"text":"When I was a child"},{"time":51250,"text":"I knew nothing about this, of course."},{"time":53398,"text":"This is me in the middle making faces."},{"time":55900,"text":"I grew up in the Paris suburbs"},{"time":58232,"text":"and I was the youngest of three children."},{"time":62121,"text":"I had a \"normal\" dad like everybody else,"},{"time":65011,"text":"apart from the fact that he was 30 years older than ..."},{"time":66956,"text":"well, he was basically old enough to be my grandfather."},{"time":70845,"text":"Anyway, he was a photographer and a street educator,"},{"time":73800,"text":"and he always taught us to obey the law very strictly."},{"time":77400,"text":"And, of course, he never talked about his past life"},{"time":79700,"text":"when he was a forger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81900,"text":"There was, however, an incident I'm going to tell you about,"},{"time":84459,"text":"that perhaps could have led me suspect something."},{"time":87376,"text":"I was in high school and got a bad grade,"},{"time":90293,"text":"a rare event for me,"},{"time":92238,"text":"so I decided to hide it from my parents."},{"time":95183,"text":"In order to do that, I set out to forge their signature."},{"time":99072,"text":"I started working on my mother's signature,"},{"time":102200,"text":"because my father's is absolutely impossible to forge."},{"time":104907,"text":"So, I got working. I took some sheets of paper"},{"time":107824,"text":"and started practicing, practicing, practicing,"},{"time":110742,"text":"until I reached what I thought was a steady hand,"},{"time":112686,"text":"and went into action."},{"time":114631,"text":"Later, while checking my school bag,"},{"time":117000,"text":"my mother got hold of my school assignment and immediately saw that the signature was forged."},{"time":120492,"text":"She yelled at me like she never had before."},{"time":122437,"text":"I went to hide in my bedroom, under the blankets,"},{"time":125354,"text":"and then I waited for my father to come back from work"},{"time":128299,"text":"with, one could say, much apprehension."},{"time":130189,"text":"I heard him come in."},{"time":132161,"text":"I remained under the blankets. He entered my room,"},{"time":136078,"text":"sat on the corner of the bed,"},{"time":138023,"text":"and he was silent, so I pulled the blanket from my head,"},{"time":140913,"text":"and when he saw me he started laughing."},{"time":143830,"text":"He was laughing so hard, he could not stop and he was holding my assignment in his hand."},{"time":146747,"text":"Then he said, \"But really, Sarah, you could have worked harder! Can't you see it's really too small?\""},{"time":151100,"text":"Indeed, it's rather small."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"I was born in Algeria."},{"time":159000,"text":"There I would hear people say my father was a \"moudjahid\""},{"time":162305,"text":"and that means \"fighter.\""},{"time":163500,"text":"Later on, in France, I loved eavesdropping on grownups' conversations,"},{"time":168084,"text":"and I would hear all sorts of stories about my father's previous life,"},{"time":171001,"text":"especially that he had \"done\" World War II,"},{"time":173919,"text":"that he had \"done\" the Algerian war."},{"time":175863,"text":"And in my head I would be thinking that \"doing\" a war meant being a soldier."},{"time":178781,"text":"But knowing my father, and how he kept saying that he was a pacifist and non-violent,"},{"time":182698,"text":"I found it very hard to picture him with a helmet and gun."},{"time":186000,"text":"And indeed, I was very far from the mark."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"One day, while my father was working on a file"},{"time":191200,"text":"for us to obtain French nationality,"},{"time":194366,"text":"I happened to see some documents"},{"time":196311,"text":"that caught my attention."},{"time":198728,"text":"These are real!"},{"time":200400,"text":"These are mine, I was born an Argentinean."},{"time":203118,"text":"But the document I happened to see"},{"time":204900,"text":"that would help us build a case for the authorities"},{"time":207007,"text":"was a document from the army"},{"time":209700,"text":"that thanked my father for his work"},{"time":212869,"text":"on behalf of the secret services."},{"time":214788,"text":"And then, suddenly, I went \"wow!\""},{"time":217705,"text":"My father, a secret agent?"},{"time":219400,"text":"It was very James Bond."},{"time":221566,"text":"I wanted to ask him questions, which he didn't answer."},{"time":226455,"text":"And later, I told myself that"},{"time":229400,"text":"one day I would have to question him."},{"time":232000,"text":"And then I became a mother and had a son,"},{"time":234151,"text":"and finally decided it was time -- that he absolutely had to talk to us."},{"time":237300,"text":"I had become a mother"},{"time":239300,"text":"and he was celebrating his 77th birthday,"},{"time":241300,"text":"and suddenly I was very, very afraid."},{"time":243600,"text":"I feared he'd go"},{"time":245848,"text":"and take his silences with him,"},{"time":247793,"text":"and take his secrets with him."},{"time":249737,"text":"I managed to convince him that it was important for us,"},{"time":252100,"text":"but possibly also for other people"},{"time":253627,"text":"that he shared his story."},{"time":255572,"text":"He decided to tell it to me"},{"time":257516,"text":"and I made a book,"},{"time":258800,"text":"from which I'm going to read you some excerpts later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261406,"text":"So, his story. My father was born in Argentina."},{"time":264323,"text":"His parents were of Russian descent."},{"time":266268,"text":"The whole family came to settle in France in the '30s."},{"time":270186,"text":"His parents were Jewish, Russian and above all, very poor."},{"time":275000,"text":"So at the age of 14 my father had to work."},{"time":278000,"text":"And with his only diploma,"},{"time":279200,"text":"his primary education certificate,"},{"time":280500,"text":"he found himself working at a dyer - dry cleaner."},{"time":283000,"text":"That's where he discovered something totally magical,"},{"time":286200,"text":"and when he talks about it, it's fascinating --"},{"time":288000,"text":"it's the magic of dyeing chemistry."},{"time":290800,"text":"During that time the war was happening"},{"time":292600,"text":"and his mother was killed when he was 15."},{"time":295468,"text":"This coincided with the time when"},{"time":298000,"text":"he threw himself body and soul into chemistry"},{"time":300000,"text":"because it was the only consolation for his sadness."},{"time":302700,"text":"All day he would ask many questions to his boss"},{"time":306164,"text":"to learn, to accumulate more and more knowledge,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and at night, when no one was looking,"},{"time":310500,"text":"he'd put his experience to practice."},{"time":312700,"text":"He was mostly interested in ink bleaching."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317800,"text":"All this to tell you"},{"time":320000,"text":"that if my father became a forger, actually,"},{"time":322500,"text":"it was almost by accident."},{"time":324500,"text":"His family was Jewish, so they were hounded."},{"time":327000,"text":"Finally they were all arrested and taken to the Drancy camp"},{"time":330000,"text":"and they managed to get out at the last minute thanks to their Argentinean papers."},{"time":333200,"text":"Well, they were out,"},{"time":334336,"text":"but they were always in danger. The big \"Jew\" stamp was still on their papers."},{"time":337253,"text":"It was my grandfather who decided they needed false documents."},{"time":340500,"text":"My father had been instilled with such respect for the law"},{"time":344000,"text":"that although he was being persecuted,"},{"time":346000,"text":"he'd never thought of false papers."},{"time":348000,"text":"But it was he who went to meet a man from the Resistance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"In those times documents had hard covers,"},{"time":353500,"text":"they were filled in by hand,"},{"time":355000,"text":"and they stated your job."},{"time":358000,"text":"In order to survive, he needed"},{"time":360200,"text":"to be working. He asked the man"},{"time":362200,"text":"to write \"dyer.\""},{"time":364000,"text":"Suddenly the man looked very, very interested."},{"time":367000,"text":"As a \"dyer,\" do you know how to bleach ink marks?"},{"time":370200,"text":"Of course he knew."},{"time":372500,"text":"And suddenly the man started explaining that"},{"time":374300,"text":"actually the whole Resistance had a huge problem:"},{"time":377000,"text":"even the top experts"},{"time":379600,"text":"could not manage to bleach an ink, called \"indelible,\""},{"time":383200,"text":"the \"Waterman\" blue ink."},{"time":385400,"text":"And my father immediately replied that he knew exactly"},{"time":389300,"text":"how to bleach it."},{"time":390500,"text":"Now, of course, the man was very impressed with this young man of 17"},{"time":393700,"text":"who could immediately give him the formula, so he recruited him."},{"time":397500,"text":"And actually, without knowing it, my father had invented something"},{"time":400500,"text":"we can find in every schoolchild's pencil case:"},{"time":403150,"text":"the so-called \"correction pen.\""},{"time":406500,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412000,"text":"But it was only the beginning."},{"time":413400,"text":"That's my father."},{"time":415000,"text":"As soon as he got to the lab,"},{"time":416500,"text":"even though he was the youngest,"},{"time":417900,"text":"he immediately saw that there was a problem with the making of forged documents."},{"time":420800,"text":"All the movements stopped at falsifying."},{"time":423700,"text":"But demand was ever-growing"},{"time":426300,"text":"and it was difficult to tamper with existing documents."},{"time":428900,"text":"He told himself it was necessary to make them from scratch."},{"time":430400,"text":"He started a press. He started photoengraving."},{"time":433200,"text":"He started making rubber stamps."},{"time":434800,"text":"He started inventing all kind of things --"},{"time":436600,"text":"with some materials he invented a centrifuge using a bicycle wheel."},{"time":440000,"text":"Anyway, he had to do all this"},{"time":442000,"text":"because he was completely obsessed with output."},{"time":444800,"text":"He had made a simple calculation:"},{"time":447000,"text":"In one hour he could make 30 forged documents."},{"time":450100,"text":"If he slept one hour, 30 people would die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454500,"text":"This sense of"},{"time":457500,"text":"responsibility for other people's lives when he was just 17 --"},{"time":460700,"text":"and also his guilt for being a survivor,"},{"time":463700,"text":"since he had escaped the camp when his friends had not --"},{"time":467300,"text":"stayed with him all his life."},{"time":469553,"text":"And this is maybe what explains why, for 30 years,"},{"time":472471,"text":"he continued to make false papers"},{"time":475100,"text":"at the expense of all kinds of sacrifices."},{"time":477400,"text":"I'd like to talk about those sacrifices,"},{"time":478300,"text":"because there were many."},{"time":480200,"text":"There were obviously financial sacrifices"},{"time":482700,"text":"because he always refused to be paid."},{"time":484500,"text":"To him, being paid would have meant being a mercenary."},{"time":487200,"text":"If he had accepted payment,"},{"time":488800,"text":"he wouldn't be able to say \"yes\" or \"no\""},{"time":490600,"text":"depending on what he deemed a just or unjust cause."},{"time":493000,"text":"So he was a photographer by day,"},{"time":494900,"text":"and a forger by night for 30 years."},{"time":496500,"text":"He was broke all of the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498500,"text":"Then there were the emotional sacrifices:"},{"time":501500,"text":"How can one live with a woman while having so many secrets?"},{"time":504500,"text":"How can one explain what one does at night in the lab, every single night?"},{"time":508700,"text":"Of course, there was another kind of sacrifice"},{"time":512000,"text":"involving his family that I understood much later."},{"time":515400,"text":"One day my father introduced me to my sister."},{"time":518500,"text":"He also explained to me that I had a brother, too,"},{"time":522500,"text":"and the first time I saw them I must have been three or four,"},{"time":528500,"text":"and they were 30 years older than me."},{"time":530300,"text":"They are both in their sixties now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535800,"text":"In order to write the book,"},{"time":538500,"text":"I asked my sister questions. I wanted to know who my father was,"},{"time":542000,"text":"who was the father she had known."},{"time":543500,"text":"She explained that the father that she'd had"},{"time":547600,"text":"would tell them he'd come and pick them up on Sunday to go for a walk."},{"time":551800,"text":"They would get all dressed up and wait for him,"},{"time":554400,"text":"but he would almost never come."},{"time":556200,"text":"He'd say, \"I'll call.\" He wouldn't call."},{"time":559500,"text":"And then he would not come."},{"time":561500,"text":"Then one day he totally disappeared."},{"time":564800,"text":"Time passed,"},{"time":566200,"text":"and they thought he had surely forgotten them,"},{"time":569400,"text":"at first."},{"time":571000,"text":"Then as time passed,"},{"time":572500,"text":"at the end of almost two years, they thought,"},{"time":574500,"text":"\"Well, perhaps our father has died.\""},{"time":577700,"text":"And then I understood"},{"time":580000,"text":"that asking my father so many questions"},{"time":582900,"text":"was stirring up a whole past he probably didn't feel like talking about"},{"time":585700,"text":"because it was painful."},{"time":587300,"text":"And while my half brother and sister thought they'd been abandoned,"},{"time":592000,"text":"orphaned,"},{"time":593700,"text":"my father was making false papers."},{"time":596000,"text":"And if he did not tell them, it was of course to protect them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":599500,"text":"After the liberation he made false papers"},{"time":601300,"text":"to allow the survivors of concentration camps to immigrate to Palestine"},{"time":604200,"text":"before the creation of Israel."},{"time":606100,"text":"And then, as he was a staunch anti-colonialist,"},{"time":608500,"text":"he made false papers for Algerians during the Algerian war."},{"time":612000,"text":"After the Algerian war,"},{"time":614600,"text":"at the heart of the international resistance movements,"},{"time":617200,"text":"his name circulated"},{"time":618900,"text":"and the whole world came knocking at his door."},{"time":621200,"text":"In Africa there were countries fighting for their independence:"},{"time":624700,"text":"Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Angola."},{"time":627700,"text":"And then my father connected with Nelson Mandela's anti-apartheid party."},{"time":632200,"text":"He made false papers for persecuted black South Africans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635700,"text":"There was also Latin America."},{"time":637500,"text":"My father helped those who resisted dictatorships"},{"time":640200,"text":"in the Dominican Republic, Haiti,"},{"time":642100,"text":"and then it was the turn of Brazil, Argentina, Venezuela, El Salvador, Nicaragua,"},{"time":648200,"text":"Colombia, Peru, Uruguay, Chile and Mexico."},{"time":653800,"text":"Then there was the Vietnam War."},{"time":655500,"text":"My father made false papers for the American deserters"},{"time":657800,"text":"who did not wish to take up arms against the Vietnamese."},{"time":661000,"text":"Europe was not spared either."},{"time":663000,"text":"My father made false papers for the dissidents"},{"time":665142,"text":"against Franco in Spain, Salazar in Portugal,"},{"time":668900,"text":"against the colonels' dictatorship in Greece,"},{"time":673893,"text":"and even in France."},{"time":675600,"text":"There, just once, it happened in May of 1968."},{"time":678755,"text":"My father watched, benevolently, of course,"},{"time":681400,"text":"the demonstrations of the month of May,"},{"time":684200,"text":"but his heart was elsewhere, and so was his time"},{"time":686500,"text":"because he had over 15 countries to serve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690000,"text":"Once, though, he agreed to make false papers"},{"time":692369,"text":"for someone you might recognize."},{"time":694313,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":697230,"text":"He was much younger in those days,"},{"time":698850,"text":"and my father agreed to make false papers"},{"time":701000,"text":"to enable him to come back and speak at a meeting."},{"time":704037,"text":"He told me that those false papers were the most media-relevant"},{"time":709000,"text":"and the least useful he'd had to make in all his life."},{"time":712500,"text":"But, he agreed to do it,"},{"time":714000,"text":"even though Daniel Cohn-Bendit's life was not in danger,"},{"time":717400,"text":"just because"},{"time":719595,"text":"it was a good opportunity"},{"time":721000,"text":"to mock the authorities,"},{"time":723485,"text":"and to show them that there's nothing more porous than borders --"},{"time":726500,"text":"and that ideas have no borders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731000,"text":"All my childhood,"},{"time":733000,"text":"while my friends' dads would tell them Grimm's fairy tales,"},{"time":737098,"text":"my father would tell me stories about very unassuming heroes"},{"time":740988,"text":"with unshakeable utopias"},{"time":743905,"text":"who managed to make miracles."},{"time":746822,"text":"And those heroes did not need an army behind them."},{"time":750800,"text":"Anyhow, nobody would have followed them,"},{"time":753300,"text":"except for a handful [of] men and women of conviction and courage."},{"time":756546,"text":"I understood much later"},{"time":757800,"text":"that actually it was his own story my father would tell me to get me to sleep."},{"time":761408,"text":"I asked him whether, considering the sacrifices he had to make,"},{"time":764325,"text":"he ever had any regrets."},{"time":766270,"text":"He said no."},{"time":768000,"text":"He told me that he would have been unable"},{"time":770160,"text":"to witness or submit to injustice without doing anything."},{"time":773077,"text":"He was persuaded, and he's still convinced"},{"time":776100,"text":"that another world is possible --"},{"time":778300,"text":"a world where no one would ever need a forger."},{"time":781300,"text":"He's still dreaming about it."},{"time":783300,"text":"My father"},{"time":784745,"text":"is here in the room today."},{"time":786500,"text":"His name is Adolfo Kaminsky and I'm going to ask him to stand up."},{"time":790580,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":811000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}